headline: What Will the Future of Farming Look Like? DigiKey's New Episodes of "Farm Different" Share Three Notable Outlooks
summary: DigiKey, the leading global electronic components and automation products distributor, announced the release of season 4 of its informative "Farm Different" video series. The series explores how the integration of advanced technology is reshaping and propelling the agricultural industry forward, and DigiKey is diving deep to understand its impact.
